{"id":51262,"title":"Epidemiology. Endocrine disorders in adult survivors of childhood cancer.","abstract":"A new report provides compelling evidence of the high prevalence of endocrine disorders in childhood cancer survivors, which begins soon after diagnosis and persists throughout adulthood. This finding highlights the need for awareness and education in primary care, and for specialized physicians to provide health care to adult survivors of childhood cancer.","date":"2014-05-21","categories":"Endocrine System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24709656","annotations":[{"name":"Epidemiology","weight":0.834159,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Epidemiology"},{"name":"Health care","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_care"},{"name":"Endocrine system","weight":0.793722,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Endocrine_system"},{"name":"Health","weight":0.781524,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health"},{"name":"Prevalence","weight":0.759037,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prevalence"},{"name":"Physician","weight":0.752214,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physician"},{"name":"Education","weight":0.720716,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Education"},{"name":"Primary care","weight":0.71741,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Primary_care"},{"name":"Diagnosis","weight":0.71741,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diagnosis"},{"name":"Childhood","weight":0.671548,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Childhood"},{"name":"Cancer","weight":0.621318,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cancer"},{"name":"Adult","weight":0.610939,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adult"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.600011,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Endocrinology","weight":0.560213,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedi